340
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:00,960
Then my dad went back to the city.

341
00:22:02,759 --> 00:22:03,960
I never even met him.

342
00:22:05,759 --> 00:22:07,440
I heard that in the city,

343
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,880
