346
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:24,440
If you find me so annoying, why did you have me?

347
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:27,000
You might as well have

348
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,839
just strangled me at birth.

349
00:22:32,440 --> 00:22:33,960
My wife also looks down on me.

350
00:22:36,319 --> 00:22:37,759
She scolds me all the time for no reason.

351
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:40,160
Fine, let her scold me.

352
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:42,319
But in the end, she ran off with someone else.

353
00:22:43,319 --> 00:22:45,640
If you look down on me, why did you marry me?

354
00:22:57,559 --> 00:22:59,400
In a bit, an auntie will come to pick you up.

355
00:22:59,759 --> 00:23:00,799
She'll take you to your mom.

356
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:03,240
And I have to go turn myself in.

357
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:04,559
Turn yourself in?

358
00:23:04,839 --> 00:23:06,160
What does "turn yourself in" mean?

359
00:23:06,759 --> 00:23:08,119
It means

360
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:10,759
