362
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:21,759
Let's go.

363
00:23:40,839 --> 00:23:41,880
Are you Dong Xiang?

364
00:24:30,519 --> 00:24:31,160
Hello.

365
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:32,319
Hello.

366
00:24:36,440 --> 00:24:38,440
We'd like to ask you a few questions.

367
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:39,960
Okay.

368
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:42,119
Let's talk over here.

369
00:24:48,079 --> 00:24:49,519
Are you Qiu Jie?

370
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:51,519
Yes.

371
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:56,559
Do you know this person?

372
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:01,720
Don't be afraid.

373
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:04,119
We've already taken him into custody.

374
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:07,039
Did he ever attack you?

375
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:11,359
He almost strangled me to death.

376
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:13,920
This scar on my face—

377
00:25:14,839 --> 00:25:16,880
I got it when I was escaping that time.

378
00:25:18,119 --> 00:25:19,279
Can you tell us exactly what happened?

379
00:25:20,519 --> 00:25:21,319
At that time—

380
00:25:27,920 --> 00:25:29,640
He came to see me a few times back then.

381
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:33,839
I don't even know how,

382
00:25:34,519 --> 00:25:36,279
he somehow thought we were in a relationship.

383
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:38,880
Later, during one of our conversations,

384
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:42,160
I said a couple of things to him and made him upset.

385
00:25:42,240 --> 00:25:44,640
He went crazy and started strangling me.

386
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:46,640
At that moment, I thought he was going to kill me.

387
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,119
When I woke up later,

388
00:25:51,279 --> 00:25:53,240
I was already dumped in a small ravine.

389
00:25:54,839 --> 00:25:56,240
Did you see him again after that?

390
00:25:56,599 --> 00:25:57,240
No.

391
00:26:00,119 --> 00:26:01,039
Officer,

392
00:26:02,079 --> 00:26:03,039
I'm begging you,

393
00:26:03,279 --> 00:26:04,559
I stopped doing that a long time ago.

394
00:26:05,119 --> 00:26:05,960
And look,

395
00:26:06,079 --> 00:26:07,480
I'm already married now.

396
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:09,000
Please, you absolutely can't let this get out.

397
00:26:09,039 --> 00:26:10,640
If my husband finds out,

398
00:26:10,839 --> 00:26:12,720
I wouldn't be able to face anyone anymore.

399
00:26:13,039 --> 00:26:15,039
Please, don't tell anyone for me.

400
00:26:15,119 --> 00:26:16,079
Don't worry about that.

401
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:17,960
We won't say a word.

402
00:26:20,559 --> 00:26:21,680
The first time,

403
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:25,079
I remember it was raining that day.

404
00:26:26,359 --> 00:26:27,559
At first, I dragged her.

405
00:26:28,559 --> 00:26:29,720
I was afraid of leaving traces.

406
00:26:30,519 --> 00:26:31,880
Later, I carried her on my shoulder.

407
00:26:33,039 --> 00:26:35,640
I was really scared at the time.

408
00:26:37,359 --> 00:26:40,640
I kept feeling like nowhere was safe.

409
00:26:42,039 --> 00:26:47,920
So I carried her from over there to here.

410
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:50,200
I saw

411
00:26:52,319 --> 00:26:53,960
that there was no one here.

412
00:26:54,559 --> 00:26:56,720
There happened to be a well here.

413
00:26:57,839 --> 00:27:00,039
So I threw her into the well.

414
00:27:02,319 --> 00:27:03,640
Later, with the second one,

415
00:27:05,119 --> 00:27:06,480
I didn't look for another place either.

416
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:09,039
I threw her in too.

417
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:10,799
Please identify it again.

418
00:27:24,519 --> 00:27:25,240
Is he handsome or not?

419
00:27:26,079 --> 00:27:26,559
Handsome.

420
00:27:30,759 --> 00:27:32,519
Thank you for your hard work, honey.

421
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,640
It wasn't hard.

422
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:36,400
Give me a hug.

423
00:27:44,039 --> 00:27:45,720
About giving birth,

424
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:48,640
