425
00:27:48,839 --> 00:27:50,440
If they do, they just make things worse.

426
00:27:50,559 --> 00:27:52,319
It can even leave aftereffects.

427
00:27:52,759 --> 00:27:55,720
I was in so much pain inside, I almost hit the wall.

428
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,960
If you were in there, I'd have to take care of you too.

429
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:01,400
Thank you for your hard work.

