00:28:47,039 --> 00:28:47,720
Mom.

444
00:28:49,519 --> 00:28:50,319
Qianqian.

445
00:28:50,519 --> 00:28:51,519
Who brought you here?

446
00:28:53,039 --> 00:28:53,960
Come here, take off your backpack.

447
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:55,440
Mom, what's wrong?

448
00:28:56,559 --> 00:28:57,000
Mom's fine.

449
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,359
Come here, take off your backpack.

450
00:29:01,839 --> 00:29:02,960
Have you eaten?

451
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:10,519
Mom, I want to confess something to you.

452
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:12,519
Confess?

