00:29:42,559 --> 00:29:44,039
A special task force was quickly assembled with elite officers.

463
00:29:44,039 --> 00:29:44,839
Did you see that?

464
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:46,799
Yes, I posted it.

465
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:49,319
After several months of continuous efforts,

466
00:29:49,599 --> 00:29:52,000
