00:30:55,519 --> 00:30:56,240
Why are you here?

484
00:30:56,240 --> 00:30:57,920
I came to see my sister-in-law and my nephew.

485
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,400
You had a son and didn't even tell me.

486
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:00,119
That's not cool.

487
00:31:01,319 --> 00:31:02,279
How did you find out?

488
00:31:02,599 --> 00:31:05,000
Come on, it's me. How could I not know?

489
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:06,319
Even if you don't know, I have to know.

490
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,599
Such disrespect.

491
00:31:09,319 --> 00:31:10,720
Why did you bring your silly apprentice?

492
00:31:11,119 --> 00:31:11,799
Where's the handsome one?

493
00:31:11,799 --> 00:31:12,599
Watch your mouth.

494
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:14,400
Are you leaving now?

495
00:31:15,119 --> 00:31:16,160
I'm hurrying to the station.

496
00:31:16,319 --> 00:31:17,960
I took time off to come here.

497
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:19,039
Hurry up and see me off.

498
00:31:19,119 --> 00:31:20,160
