511
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:53,200
These little hands can't touch your brother's face.

512
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:54,000
What's his name?

513
00:31:54,599 --> 00:31:57,160
We haven't named him yet. Why don't you pick one?

514
00:31:57,759 --> 00:31:58,599
Does he have a nickname?

515
00:31:58,799 --> 00:32:00,599
Diandian. His mom picked it.

516
00:32:01,599 --> 00:32:02,480
Liu Yidian

517
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,160
What does it mean?

518
00:32:04,519 --> 00:32:07,240
Leave a little in everything you do and in how you act.

519
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:10,599
He's crying.

520
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:11,759
Let me, let me, let me.

521
00:32:11,759 --> 00:32:12,920
Let me do it. I'll do it, I'll do it.

522
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:15,519
Look at the name you picked.

523
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:16,640
Isn't this a good name?

524
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:18,000
Is he hungry?

525
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,240
Here you go, sir.

526
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:27,960
Thank you.

527
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:31,160
Come on.

528
00:32:35,559 --> 00:32:36,359
Right here.

529
00:32:38,079 --> 00:32:39,240
Do you see that building?

530
00:32:39,759 --> 00:32:41,440
I see it. What's up?

531
00:32:42,759 --> 00:32:44,960
Count from the bottom up to the nineteenth floor.

532
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:46,920
How many floors are there in total?

533
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:47,640
Twenty.

534
00:32:48,359 --> 00:32:50,559
Then you could've just had me count from the top down.

535
00:32:50,599 --> 00:32:52,599
No, you have to count from the bottom up.

536
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:58,200
One, two, three, four, five...

537
00:32:59,759 --> 00:33:02,039
What are you doing, making me count to the nineteenth floor?

538
00:33:02,559 --> 00:33:03,680
You brought me here

539
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:05,400
